2
00:00:09,300 --> 00:00:14,940
♪I'm the tiniest dust in the world♪

3
00:00:15,020 --> 00:00:17,820
♪With all the sincerity I can muster♪

4
00:00:18,020 --> 00:00:20,860
♪For your kiss after the tears♪

5
00:00:20,980 --> 00:00:23,100
♪Through the storm♪

6
00:00:23,220 --> 00:00:27,180
♪I'd like to travel with you♪

7
00:00:28,940 --> 00:00:30,370
[Beauty Strategy Season 1]

8
00:00:30,370 --> 00:00:35,050
[Adapted from The Spirit Empress
by TUTU on Kuaikan World]

9
00:00:35,050 --> 00:00:38,000
[Episode 2]
[Showing True Form in Public]

10
00:00:51,380 --> 00:00:52,340
What do you mean, Your Majesty?

11
00:00:52,940 --> 00:00:54,020
Kill yourself.

12
00:01:05,540 --> 00:01:06,180
Your Majesty,

13
00:01:06,740 --> 00:01:08,060
sorry, I can't do that.

14
00:01:08,420 --> 00:01:09,580
I've risen from humble beginnings.

15
00:01:09,900 --> 00:01:11,100
When you force me to kill myself,

16
00:01:11,460 --> 00:01:12,380
I won't dare to disobey you.

17
00:01:12,780 --> 00:01:14,060
But if I die,

18
00:01:15,220 --> 00:01:17,940
you may be in danger, Your Majesty.

19
00:01:20,180 --> 00:01:21,700
You're just a mere Lady.

20
00:01:22,020 --> 00:01:23,940
How would your death threaten my life?

21
00:01:24,260 --> 00:01:25,620
The Royal Empress Dowager
has command over the military

22
00:01:26,060 --> 00:01:27,180
and takes charge of the court.

23
00:01:27,820 --> 00:01:29,060
Your Majesty, if you kill the concubine

24
00:01:29,220 --> 00:01:30,900
given by Her Royal Highness
just to vent your anger,

25
00:01:31,140 --> 00:01:32,620
you will infuriate her

26
00:01:32,940 --> 00:01:34,180
and bring turbulence to the court.

27
00:01:34,460 --> 00:01:37,060
For you, it is hardly worth the candle.

28
00:01:38,340 --> 00:01:39,580
You're just a slave,

29
00:01:40,100 --> 00:01:42,540
yet you can talk clearly and logically
about the situation of the court

30
00:01:43,220 --> 00:01:45,220
and remain calm
when you're forced to kill yourself.

31
00:01:46,580 --> 00:01:48,260
Are you really a mere slave?

32
00:01:50,020 --> 00:01:51,700
I'm so definite

33
00:01:53,060 --> 00:01:54,100
only because Your Majesty

34
00:01:54,900 --> 00:01:56,660
doesn't really want to kill me.

35
00:01:57,060 --> 00:01:58,500
You're just testing me.

36
00:02:08,980 --> 00:02:09,540
Mother!

37
00:02:16,860 --> 00:02:17,740
Shuoye?

38
00:02:19,300 --> 00:02:20,060
She looks just like her.

39
00:02:21,380 --> 00:02:22,900
Isn't she supposed to be dead?

40
00:02:24,580 --> 00:02:26,380
Her Royal Highness
indeed has a good taste.

41
00:02:26,940 --> 00:02:29,780
She's chosen
such a gorgeous slave for me.

42
00:02:39,660 --> 00:02:41,340
I don't work for Her Royal Highness.

43
00:02:57,060 --> 00:02:57,940
Are you sure?

44
00:02:59,380 --> 00:03:00,540
If you don't believe me, Your Majesty,

45
00:03:01,940 --> 00:03:03,540
I will prove it to you.

46
00:03:07,260 --> 00:03:09,700
I will be your sword.

47
00:03:17,500 --> 00:03:19,060
Be my sword?

48
00:03:19,860 --> 00:03:20,700
Do you think you deserve to do that?

49
00:03:21,380 --> 00:03:21,860
Your Majesty.

50
00:03:21,940 --> 00:03:22,500
Somebody.

51
00:03:23,500 --> 00:03:25,540
Send Lady Ling to the Tinghan Palace.

52
00:03:30,820 --> 00:03:34,670
[Tinghan Palace]

53
00:03:39,020 --> 00:03:41,300
Other maids enjoy a better life
when their ladies are promoted.

54
00:03:41,580 --> 00:03:43,500
But I'm assigned
to such a terrible place.

55
00:04:01,540 --> 00:04:04,820
Now, I should call you Lady Ling, huh?

56
00:04:10,300 --> 00:04:11,140
What are you doing?

57
00:04:11,820 --> 00:04:13,860
Lady An, don't forget

58
00:04:14,140 --> 00:04:15,260
that we're equals now.

59
00:04:16,020 --> 00:04:17,500
You have no right to punish me.

60
00:04:23,460 --> 00:04:25,940
The other day, I had you battered.

61
00:04:26,220 --> 00:04:27,980
Why do you look unharmed now?

62
00:04:28,940 --> 00:04:31,100
You must be from the evil Spirit clan.

63
00:04:33,420 --> 00:04:34,660
I don't know what you're talking about.

64
00:04:35,020 --> 00:04:38,380
The Spirit clan is a taboo here.

65
00:04:38,700 --> 00:04:40,540
Any of them must be executed.

66
00:04:49,460 --> 00:04:50,620
I work for the Royal Empress Dowager.

67
00:04:51,420 --> 00:04:53,100
Don't you fear
you'll offend Her Royal Highness?

68
00:04:54,380 --> 00:04:55,860
If you really worked
for Her Royal Highness,

69
00:04:56,020 --> 00:04:57,820
you wouldn't end up in this place.

70
00:05:09,860 --> 00:05:10,580
Lady An,

71
00:05:11,380 --> 00:05:12,340
what are you doing?

72
00:05:16,420 --> 00:05:16,980
Your Majesty.

73
00:05:26,460 --> 00:05:27,300
Lady An,

74
00:05:27,740 --> 00:05:29,860
how dare you punish her
without my permission?

75
00:05:30,420 --> 00:05:32,060
Your Majesty, I'm just...

76
00:05:32,060 --> 00:05:33,020
If it happens again,

77
00:05:33,420 --> 00:05:34,900
you'll be severely punished.

78
00:05:35,060 --> 00:05:37,300
I'm wrong. Please forgive me,
Your Majesty.

79
00:05:50,740 --> 00:05:51,940
Lady Ling, are you hurt?

80
00:05:53,740 --> 00:05:54,900
I'm fine.

81
00:05:55,740 --> 00:05:57,020
Thank you for caring, Your Majesty.

82
00:06:00,980 --> 00:06:02,300
Stop being mad at me,

83
00:06:03,500 --> 00:06:03,980
will you?

84
00:06:09,900 --> 00:06:10,940
I...

85
00:06:12,580 --> 00:06:13,380
Yes, Your Majesty.

86
00:06:16,500 --> 00:06:17,580
Get lost now.

87
00:06:20,940 --> 00:06:21,860
Thank you, Your Majesty.

88
00:06:27,260 --> 00:06:30,140
Why did he change his mind so quickly?

89
00:06:32,580 --> 00:06:33,780
Your Majesty, isn't it easy for you

90
00:06:34,300 --> 00:06:35,620
to get rid of Lady Ling?

91
00:06:36,060 --> 00:06:38,420
The Royal Empress Dowager humiliated me
with a humble salve on purpose.

92
00:06:38,780 --> 00:06:40,300
If I kill her personally,

93
00:06:40,980 --> 00:06:42,740
she'll have a reason to dethrone me.

94
00:06:42,740 --> 00:06:44,900
Then Your Majesty,
why do you favor Lady Ling this much?

95
00:06:47,860 --> 00:06:48,780
In the Imperial Palace,

96
00:06:49,180 --> 00:06:52,020
I only favor the deadliest poison.

97
00:06:52,820 --> 00:06:53,700
To get rid of her,

98
00:06:54,580 --> 00:06:55,940
I don't need to do it myself.

99
00:07:06,860 --> 00:07:08,500
Lady Ling, you do know the drill.

100
00:07:09,020 --> 00:07:10,820
You've actually come to pay
your respects to Concubine Huan.

101
00:07:13,180 --> 00:07:14,380
Today,

102
00:07:14,620 --> 00:07:17,620
I have a little surprise for you.

103
00:07:19,900 --> 00:07:21,780
Concubine Huan is here!

104
00:07:30,860 --> 00:07:32,620
- Greetings, Your Grace.
- Greetings, Your Grace.

105
00:07:46,380 --> 00:07:49,100
You're Lady Ling
chosen by Her Royal Highness, huh?

106
00:07:49,500 --> 00:07:52,140
I, Lingzhi, show my greetings to you,
Your Grace.

107
00:07:54,580 --> 00:07:55,140
Come over.

108
00:08:04,700 --> 00:08:05,980
So, she's Concubine Huan
from the Phantom clan

109
00:08:05,980 --> 00:08:06,940
who's got a peace-making marriage,

110
00:08:07,540 --> 00:08:09,740
the woman in charge of the harem.

111
00:08:12,660 --> 00:08:14,420
You're gorgeous, indeed.

112
00:08:19,300 --> 00:08:20,100
Take your seats.

113
00:08:20,860 --> 00:08:22,180
- Thank you, Your Grace.
- Thank you, Your Grace.

114
00:08:30,340 --> 00:08:31,260
Your Grace,

115
00:08:31,420 --> 00:08:33,940
I got a good wine
from outside the palace.

116
00:08:34,020 --> 00:08:35,340
It helps to retain youthful looks.

117
00:08:35,460 --> 00:08:36,620
It's especially for you, Your Grace.

118
00:08:36,900 --> 00:08:38,380
This wine is from outside the palace.

119
00:08:38,860 --> 00:08:40,700
Her Grace will not risk tasting it.

120
00:08:41,300 --> 00:08:43,540
Your Grace, you may take it back.

121
00:08:44,820 --> 00:08:46,140
Your Grace, if you worry,

122
00:08:46,420 --> 00:08:47,860
you can have someone else taste it.

123
00:08:51,980 --> 00:08:53,620
Lady Ling used to be a slave.

124
00:08:53,940 --> 00:08:55,900
She must have
some experience of tasting wine.

125
00:09:04,780 --> 00:09:05,940
Please, Lady Ling.

126
00:09:10,220 --> 00:09:11,650
Anyone of the Spirit clan
will show their true forms

127
00:09:11,650 --> 00:09:12,340
after drinking this wine.

128
00:09:12,340 --> 00:09:13,980
Your Grace, you can give it a try.

129
00:09:22,300 --> 00:09:24,260
Your Grace, I can't hold my liquor.

130
00:09:24,580 --> 00:09:25,700
So, I'm afraid I can't
taste the wine for you.

131
00:09:27,340 --> 00:09:29,020
With the love of His Majesty,

132
00:09:29,180 --> 00:09:30,500
you just don't want
to do it for Her Grace, do you?

133
00:09:33,140 --> 00:09:36,260
Lady An, you're also
telling Her Grace what to do

134
00:09:36,900 --> 00:09:38,940
based on the love of His Majesty.

135
00:09:39,380 --> 00:09:40,500
Why do you hate me this much?

136
00:09:41,060 --> 00:09:44,020
In fear of losing His Majesty's love?

137
00:09:55,860 --> 00:09:57,340
How arrogant and domineering you are!

138
00:09:57,660 --> 00:09:59,620
You're totally disrespecting Her Grace.

139
00:10:00,020 --> 00:10:01,180
You humble slave,

140
00:10:01,820 --> 00:10:02,460
I'm going to kill you!

141
00:10:02,460 --> 00:10:03,100
How presumptuous!

142
00:10:18,740 --> 00:10:20,300
You're just a Lady,

143
00:10:21,300 --> 00:10:23,140
yet you dare make a scene in my place.

144
00:10:40,180 --> 00:10:40,860
Somebody.

145
00:10:42,100 --> 00:10:43,580
Take Lady An away

146
00:10:43,900 --> 00:10:46,220
and punish her with "Blooming".

147
00:10:46,340 --> 00:10:46,860
- Yes.
- Yes.

148
00:10:46,860 --> 00:10:47,820
Please spare me, Your Grace!

149
00:10:48,740 --> 00:10:49,820
Please spare me, Your Grace!

150
00:10:49,980 --> 00:10:51,220
I don't dare to do it again!

151
00:10:51,540 --> 00:10:53,020
I won't do it again!

152
00:10:54,020 --> 00:10:57,260
If anyone dares to be haughty
because of His Majesty's love

153
00:10:57,780 --> 00:10:59,460
and disrespect superiors,

154
00:11:01,820 --> 00:11:02,380
this is...

155
00:11:04,020 --> 00:11:05,420
how she'll end up.

156
00:11:06,780 --> 00:11:09,660
- Yes, Your Grace.
- Yes, Your Grace.

157
00:11:26,180 --> 00:11:26,980
Lady Ling,

158
00:11:27,940 --> 00:11:28,740
the wine...

159
00:11:30,020 --> 00:11:31,900
I'm giving it to you.

160
00:11:33,580 --> 00:11:37,300
Will you drink it or not?

161
00:11:59,540 --> 00:12:01,100
I can't suppress my true form anymore.

162
00:12:01,820 --> 00:12:02,500
Oh, no.

163
00:12:02,860 --> 00:12:04,260
Once others know
that I'm of the Spirit clan,

164
00:12:04,820 --> 00:12:06,180
I'm doomed.

165
00:12:24,250 --> 00:12:26,970
♪My eyebrows are outlined
against the rain♪

166
00:12:27,210 --> 00:12:30,710
♪Lovesickness tastes like bitter wine♪

167
00:12:31,730 --> 00:12:34,410
♪The wind signs through destiny♪

168
00:12:34,810 --> 00:12:38,050
♪Love and hate are forever gone♪

169
00:12:38,210 --> 00:12:41,850
♪Don't ask where I'm going♪

170
00:12:42,290 --> 00:12:45,490
♪I won't change my love for you♪

171
00:12:45,730 --> 00:12:49,210
♪My destination is my fate,
my obsession is to wait♪

172
00:12:49,490 --> 00:12:53,290
♪I'm just destined to wander♪

173
00:12:53,930 --> 00:12:56,970
♪If I'm always greedy♪

174
00:12:57,330 --> 00:13:00,690
♪You're what I want for this life♪

175
00:13:01,370 --> 00:13:04,410
♪Yet you don't even look back
when the song ends♪

176
00:13:04,690 --> 00:13:08,170
♪Who gets stuck in the dream with me?♪

177
00:13:08,170 --> 00:13:11,730
♪Old memories never yield♪

178
00:13:11,850 --> 00:13:15,570
♪Under the spring breeze,
the flowers bloom as before♪

179
00:13:15,770 --> 00:13:19,250
♪When clouds are dispersed,
I will disappear♪

180
00:13:19,530 --> 00:13:22,610
♪However far away I stay,
I'm always who I am♪

181
00:13:23,280 --> 00:13:25,550
♪The moonlight gently falls
into your eyes♪
